comments: Porter Jr. (HOU) maintains a legal guarding position while contesting Dinwiddie's (DAL) shot attempt.
Wood (DAL) maintains a legal guarding position while contesting Smith Jr.'s (HOU) shot attempt.
Smith Jr. (HOU) and Wood (DAL) come together and the contact during the pick is marginal.
Sengun (HOU) cleanly dislodges the ball from Doncic (DAL), any ensuing contact is incidental.
Porter Jr. (HOU) goes through Hardaway Jr.'s (DAL) space and dislodges him from his legal guarding position at the end of his drive toward the rim.
Smith Jr.'s (HOU) hand slides off of Wood's (DAL) upper body as he is moving through the pick.
Martin Jr. (HOU) slightly extends his arm into Dinwiddie (DAL) as he is rolling toward the rim.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Martin Jr. (HOU) loses control of the ball and is the last to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
Garuba (HOU) wraps Wood (DAL) and affects his ability to get to the rebound.
Dinwiddie (DAL) firms up in Smith Jr.'s (HOU) path and marginal contact occurs as both players come together during the pick.
Pinson (DAL) and Porter Jr. (HOU) come together and marginal contact occurs as Porter Jr. is running through the lane.
Martin Jr. (HOU) commits a take foul on Hardaway Jr. (DAL).
Sengun (HOU) slightly extends his arm into Doncic (DAL) as both players go for the loose ball.
